{
  "texts": [
    "Embryoid body development.",
    "Data preprocessing.",
    "We followed Scanpy's workflow to process the raw count matrix.",
    "As a first step, we filtered out genes expressed in fewer than ten cells (scanpy.pp.filter_genes with min_cells=10).",
    "Following, we removed cells with more than 17,500 counts, cells for which more than 15% of counts originate from mitochondrial genes and cells expressing more than 3,500 genes."
  ]
}